---
title: Double Mumbai Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Garlic Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: This gorgeous plate of colour doesn't just look good - it's a nutritionally balanced combo of garlic yoghurt, succulent
chicken, rainbow roasted veggies and crunchy almonds. Flavour is just written all over it.
